.TH "sfwbar-idle" "1" "" ""
.SH Name
sfwbar-idle \- Sfwbar Idle notifier module
.sp
Filename: idle.so
.sp
Requires: none
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
The idle notifier module, provides support for idle triggers, i.e. triggers
that are emitted if the user has been idle for a specified period of time.
.SH Triggers
.sp
The idle module defines trigger \fIresumed\fP\&. This trigger is emitted on the first
user interaction after a timeout. Timeout triggers are defined using the
\fIIdleTimeout\fP action.
.SH Functions
.SS IdleTimeout(Trigger, Timeout)
.sp
Create a new trigger with a name \fITrigger\fP that will be emitted after \fITimeout\fP
seconds of idleness. I.e. \fIIdleTimeout(\(dqtimeout1\(dq, 10)\fP\&. A trigger can be
removed by calling this function again with a \fITimeout\fP value of zero.
